{
  "stem": "3453.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I came up to him, and I said, I'm the daughter of so and so.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tears stood up in his eyes, and he said, they are like my kids, and they will stay with us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then he said it was the law because he was the leader of the group .",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- the people from the village had great respect for him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they knew that if something-- if they will do something bad, they will be paid back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the story about this-- and all of a sudden, while we were down there, a-- a teacher appeared into this remote village in the woods, a remote village.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The village consisted, I don't know, a few hundred maybe residents, maybe not even that many, a small-- all of a sudden appeared a-- a-- a teacher that supposedly, the Germans are sending him down there to organize a school.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All of a sudden, they were preoccupied to give schooling and to educate people, when the killing and the murdering was going on in the thousands and in the thousands.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew right away that we must watch this foreigner, this stranger.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who is he and what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were right away suspicious who he was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We find out exactly where he was asleep, in what house he was living.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we saw him going to Sarny, to the town in the middle of-- of the-- of the week, coming back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was unheard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you don't go around at that time when the war was raging, and the wars are going.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew right away he wants to tip off the Germans and to find out there are Jews, there are Partisans, whatever that.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
